<div style="border: solid 5px #999999; background:#a0bdbf; padding: 0px; margin: auto; width: 640px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>&#171; <a href="/archival-document-hsa-008-advent">Archival Document -- HSA-008-Advent</a> || Black Sunrise || Operation AEON DAWN &#187;</strong></p>
</div>
